youtube-cc-dl

youtube-cc-dl downloads a closed caption from YouTube video and
converts it into SubRipt text file format.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc WWW::YouTube::CC

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=youtube-cc-dl

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/youtube-cc-dl

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/youtube-cc-dl

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/youtube-cc-dl/


